%p
  .strong= @market_post.content.title
  %br
  .strong Cost:
  = @market_post.cost

= (@market_post.content.raw_content).html_safe

- contact_string = contact_display(@market_post)
- if contact_string.present?
  %p 
    .strong Contact: 
    #{contact_string}

- if @base_uri.present?
  - url = "#{@base_uri}/contents/#{@market_post.content.id}/market_posts/#{@market_post.id}"
- else
  - url = "http://www.dailyuv.com/uvmarket"

See details and discover more in dailyUV Market: 
= link_to url, url
